-- Turkey's Yildiz Holding to sell stake in Gozde private equity
-- 
-- Wed Aug 06, 2014 11:08AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Aug 6 (Reuters) - Turkey's Yildiz Holding will sell up to 10 percent of its private equity firm Gozde Girisim <GOZDE.IS> to foreign investors within one year, the company said on Wednesday.

Yildiz also said in its statement to Istanbul stock exchange that it mandated Unlu Securities for the sale.